data.description: Welcome home! Located in the rapidly expanding Northwest region of Katy, TX, you'll find yourself wonderfully situated under 10 minutes away from conveniences, such as Target, Kroger, Home Goods, and a plethora of Restaurants and Gas Stations! From the outside-in, this home has been spectacularly maintained! Easy to clean, large, wood-look tile floors have been added in all main areas from the front door to the back, so bring your big dogs with no worries! With features like a Mud nook right inside the garage entry door to a dedicated office space, this Pulte-built home brings affordable, practical livability to a new level! It's no easy task to find a 5 bedroom 3 full bathroom home with over 3,000 square feet of living space in Katy for LESS THAN $450,000, so this is the ONE! You'll enjoy a covered back patio in this oversized backyard with no direct back neighbors! We left a few extras out of the photos, so you'll want to come check this one out in person right away!
